{"tid":1940592,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"意大利疫情開始放緩","createTime":"2020-03-24T01:09:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T04:01:19.000Z","uid":134071,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"560282b4d7b8f9bcb1acdbb2e62bfa743e4b6cd1","tid":1940592,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T01:09:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1516388-20200324.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1516388-20200324.htm&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1u6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=0f0371d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1516388-20200324.htm&h=14a842be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1516388-20200324.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n意大利新增死亡病例連續第二日下跌<br />\n2020-03-24 HKT 02:18<br />\n<br />\n意大利再多601宗新型肺炎<strong>死亡病例，數字連續第二日下跌</strong>，亦是自上星期四以來，死亡人數增幅最少的一日，累計6077人不治。<br />\n<br />\n確診病例就新增4789宗至63900多宗，增幅8%，<strong>是自疫情上月21日爆發以來最低增幅</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n意大利政府星期一起進一步收緊「封城」措施，禁止民眾在國內旅遊，所有非必要生產暫停。總理孔特說，國家的社會及經濟實力受到威脅，需要國民共同努力，又說雖然疫情似乎有所緩和，但民眾不能夠放低戒備。"},{"pid":"eac43df133203530ee6c4b88c5b685cdadb7eee3","tid":1940592,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T01:09:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e14a126583138999583f54bf10a2865bf666e54","tid":1940592,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T01:11:16.000Z","msg":"忍 14 日再封關到退潮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf6d8673fa644d768b4f19cdc6fd534d6dd744ba","tid":1940592,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T01:11:37.000Z","msg":"咪燈，thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0